Running:

sudo python measure.py

For continuous measurement run:

watch -n 1 sudo python measure.py

Expected result looks similar to this:

Temperature:  18.9 deg C
Pressure:  1013.39  hPa


Connecting:

BMP pin : RPi pin
========:===============
VIN     : 17  (3v3)
3vo     : N/C
GND     : 25  (GND)
SCLK    : 23  (GPIO11)
SDO     : 21  (GPIO09; MISO)
SDI     : 19  (GPIO10; MOSI)
CS      : 24  (GPIO08; CE0)
